data.description: This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with RV access and a HUGE backyard has recently been remolded! This home is move-in ready offering new interior and exterior paint, new flooring, granite countertops, brand new appliances and much more! Don't miss out on this opportunity to own in an established Atwater neighborhood, close to shopping and restaurants.
